src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Evening' game
04 Nov 2019, 01:08 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 4 Evening" game were:
2-7-7-2
(two, seven, seven, two)
